Chosen Persona: Food Delivery Partners (Zomato / Swiggy)
Why Food Delivery?

Highest outdoor exposure — riders spend 4–8 hours daily on roads
Most sensitive to real-time weather (rain immediately halts deliveries)
Largest gig worker pool in India (~5 million active delivery partners)
Short delivery windows make per-hour income loss most financially painful
Platform order volume drops directly and measurably during disruptions


User Persona: Ravi, 28 — Swiggy Delivery Partner, Chennai
📍 Zone         : Tambaram, Chennai
⏰ Working Hours: 10 AM – 10 PM (10 hrs/day, 6 days/week)
💰 Weekly Income: ₹3,500 – ₹4,200
🏍️ Vehicle      : Two-wheeler (petrol)
📱 Device       : Android mid-range, basic UPI literacy
🌧️ Key Risks    : Northeast monsoon (Oct–Dec), heatwaves (Apr–Jun)

